# Validation Workflow

**Run `make check` before every commit. Zero tolerance for linting errors.**

Pre-commit checklist:

1. `make check` — lint all modified files (shell + markdown)
2. `make test-smoke` — smoke tests (30s)
3. `make test` — full test suite if changes are non-trivial

Fix all linting errors before committing. If adding new patterns, update AGENTS.md.
